gsjj_am_0040_201904","isCollect":"0","subPrimPic":"","refAnswer":"C","fourthPic":"","discPic":"","second":"每分钟18～20次","subjectTypeEname":"am","originalText":"","thirdPic":"","secondPic":"","third":"吸气时间短，呼气时间长","fifthPic":"","audioFiles":"","children":[],"primPic":"","fifth":"用鼻吸气，用鼻呼气","fourth":"吸气时收腹，呼气时挺腹","answerPic":"","first":"每次进行30～60分钟"},{"groupCodePrimQuestion":"","primQuestion":"患者，女，40岁。毛绒玩具车间工人，有哮喘史5年。防止哮喘发作最有效的方法是","discription":"防止哮喘发作最有效的方法是脱离变应原，故本题选A。","firstPic":"","questionCode":"id_phhlzhggsjj_am_0049_201904","isCollect":"0","subPrimPic":"","refAnswer":"A","fourthPic":"","discPic":"","second":"药物治疗","subjectTypeEname":"am","originalText":"","thirdPic":"","secondPic":"","third":"免疫治疗","fifthPic":"","audioFiles":"","children":[],"primPic":"","fifth":"长期治疗","fourth":"对症治疗","answerPic":"","first":"脱离变应原"},{"groupCodePrimQuestion":"","primQuestion":"患者，女，55岁。因发作性胸闷、咳嗽就诊，诊为支气管哮喘。医嘱予糖皮质激素吸入治疗，下列用药指导中正确的是","discription":"采用排除法。","firstPic":"","questionCode":"id_phhlzhggsjj_am_0053_201904","isCollect":"0","subPrimPic":"","refAnswer":"D","fourthPic":"","discPic":"","second":"“如果哮喘症状缓解，即可停止用药。”","subjectTypeEname":"am","originalText":"","thirdPic":"","secondPic":"","third":"“吸入激素不会有任何副作用。”","fifthPic":"","audioFiles":"","children":[],"primPic":"","fifth":"“如果您要进行运动，可在此前预防性吸入激素。”","fourth":"“吸入激素后要漱口。”","answerPic":"","first":"“吸入激素的主要作用是快速缓解症状。”"},{"groupCodePrimQuestion":"","primQuestion":"患者，女，69岁。慢性肺心病急性发作，患者出现头痛、昼眠夜醒、神志恍惚应考虑","discription":"肺源性心脏病(简称肺心病)患者出现头痛、昼眠夜醒、神智恍惚症状，应考虑出现了肺性脑病，故本题选D。","firstPic":"","questionCode":"id_phhlzhggsjj_am_0075_201904","isCollect":"0","subPrimPic":"","refAnswer":"D","fourthPic":"","discPic":"","second":"呼吸性酸中毒","subjectTypeEname":"am","originalText":"","thirdPic":"","secondPic":"","third":"休克早期","fifthPic":"","audioFiles":"","children":[],"primPic":"","fifth":"DIC","fourth":"肺性脑病","answerPic":"","first":"窒息先兆"},{"groupCodePrimQuestion":"","primQuestion":"患者，男，31岁。胸部受伤，急诊入院。经吸氧，呼吸困难无好转，有发绀及休克体征。查体：左胸饱满，叩之鼓音，听诊呼吸音消失，皮下气肿明显